item.title: Hotel Management Website
item.description:
Developed Hotel Management Website with SpringBoot in distributed and microservices architecture.

Use Solr for full-text search, Redis}to implement distributed lock, ActiveMQ for message queue, and use Tomcat, Nginx to deploy. Familiar with the use of Postman, Junit and Jmeters.

item.title: NILM
item.description:
Joined A/Prof. Du’s lab to work on a non-intrusive electricity load monitoring (NILM) project predicting the electric vehicles’ electricity usage from the waveform graph of households.

Finished data cleaning and reproduced the AFHMM and machine learning Benchmarks.

Designed a semi-supervised deep learning algorithm to solve the problem.
